Text: how do I register, and do you have to??... I entered the serial number, but which e-mail adress do i have to enter???
How the **** did u get the registration to work?

This site describes how to get past registration:
http://www.9down.com/story.php?sid=6773

note: I have done some checking and this program process/pid when running uses port 3561 and 3562 to validate its registry info from the registration server. So I beleive blocking these ports will prevent unregistration as well. Then It is blocked regardless of what the server name is or its ip. I captured this data by running a netstat -b on a test machine running the software when a request was made. --- enjoy
